    <entry>
      <title>tabby Spring Data MongoDB SPEL</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/28/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/28/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Source"><a href="#Source" class="headerlink" title="Source"></a>Source</h2><p>即确定<code>@Query</code>在哪被Spring Data MongoDB解析。</p><blockquote><p>tabby 目前不支持对象代理查询</p></blockquote><p>处理的Interceptor为<code>QueryExecutorMethodInterceptor</code>，在 invoke 处设置断点，然后走向了<code>AbstractMongoQuery#doExecute</code>，处理 query 并返回查询结果，可当为 Source</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">protected</span> Object <span class="title function_">doExecute</span><span class="params">(MongoQueryMethod method, ResultProcessor processor, ConvertingParameterAccessor accessor, <span class="meta">@Nullable</span> Class&lt;?&gt; typeToRead)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Query</span> <span class="variable">query</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="built_in">this</span>.createQuery(accessor);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.applyQueryMetaAttributesWhenPresent(query);</span><br><span class="line">        query = <span class="built_in">this</span>.applyAnnotatedDefaultSortIfPresent(query);</span><br><span class="line">        query = <span class="built_in">this</span>.applyAnnotatedCollationIfPresent(query, accessor);</span><br><span class="line">        ExecutableFindOperation.FindWithQuery&lt;?&gt; find = typeToRead == <span class="literal">null</span> ? <span class="built_in">this</span>.executableFind : <span class="built_in">this</span>.executableFind.as(typeToRead);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">this</span>.getExecution(accessor, (ExecutableFindOperation.FindWithQuery)find).execute(query);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>accessor</code>：注解方法的函数形参，即 keyword</li><li><code>query</code>：<code>@Query</code>的值</li></ul><p><img src="/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL.assets/image-20220728093545908.png" alt="image-20220728093545908"></p><h2 id="Sink"><a href="#Sink" class="headerlink" title="Sink"></a>Sink</h2><p><code>parseExpression()</code></p><h2 id="查询语句"><a href="#查询语句" class="headerlink" title="查询语句"></a>查询语句</h2><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>Source是AbstractMongoQuery#doExecute</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">match</span>(source:<span class="keyword">Method</span>&#123;CLASSNAME:&quot;org.springframework.data.mongodb.repository.query.AbstractMongoQuery&quot;, NAME:&quot;doExecute&quot;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>Sink是parseExpression方法</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">match</span>((sink:<span class="keyword">Method</span>&#123;NAME:&quot;parseExpression&quot;&#125;) <span class="operator">&lt;</span><span class="operator">-</span> [:<span class="keyword">CALL</span><span class="operator">|</span>ALIAS] <span class="operator">-</span> (m:<span class="keyword">Method</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span>调用路径查询</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">call</span> apoc.algo.allSimplePaths(m, source, &quot;&lt;CALL|ALIAS&quot;, <span class="number">10</span>) yield path </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="operator">*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apoc.algo.allSimplePaths(startNode :: NODE?, endNode :: NODE?, </span><br><span class="line">relationshipTypesAndDirections :: STRING?, maxNodes :: INTEGER?) :: </span><br><span class="line">(path :: PATH?)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>（有点奇怪，sink 为 startnode？</p><p><img src="/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL.assets/graph.png" alt="graph"></p><p>要么走 &lt;init&gt; 到 bindableValueFor，要么走 toDocument</p><p><img src="/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL.assets/image-20220728103822521.png" alt="image-20220728103822521"></p><h2 id="进一步分析"><a href="#进一步分析" class="headerlink" title="进一步分析"></a>进一步分析</h2><p>在<code>ParameterBindingJsonReader</code>中</p><p><img src="/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL.assets/image-20220728094253097.png" alt="image-20220728094253097"></p><p>之前构造的 json 不会进入 bindableVauleFor ，后发现只要进入就会解析 SPEL</p><h3 id="bindableVauleFor"><a href="#bindableVauleFor" class="headerlink" title="bindableVauleFor"></a>bindableVauleFor</h3><p>走到<code>evaluateExpression()</code>中。<code>evaluateExpression()</code>函数会一路调用到 Sink 点<code>parseExpression()</code></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span> BindableValue <span class="title function_">bindableValueFor</span><span class="params">(JsonToken token)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//JSON是未闭合的字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (token.getType().equals(JsonTokenType.UNQUOTED_STRING)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//正则 [\?:]#\&#123;.*\&#125;。需要形如 ?#&#123;xxx&#125; 或者 :#&#123;xxx&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Matcher</span> <span class="variable">regexMatcher</span> <span class="operator">=</span> EXPRESSION_BINDING_PATTERN.matcher(tokenValue);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (regexMatcher.find()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">binding</span> <span class="operator">=</span> regexMatcher.group();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">expression</span> <span class="operator">=</span> binding.substring(<span class="number">3</span>, binding.length() - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//正则 \?(\d+)。形如 ?0</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">Matcher</span> <span class="variable">inSpelMatcher</span> <span class="operator">=</span> PARAMETER_BINDING_PATTERN.matcher(expression);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span> (inSpelMatcher.find()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">index</span> <span class="operator">=</span> computeParameterIndex(inSpelMatcher.group());</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">//将表达式中形如?0 替换成真实值</span></span><br><span class="line">                expression = expression.replace(inSpelMatcher.group(), getBindableValueForIndex(index).toString());</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">//【！】执行SpEL解析</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">Object</span> <span class="variable">value</span> <span class="operator">=</span> evaluateExpression(expression);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ......</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以下注解均可：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Query(&quot;&#123;id : ?#&#123;?0&#125;&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Query(&quot;&#123;id : :#&#123;?0&#125;&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL.assets/image-20220728110545718.png" alt="image-20220728110545718"></p><p><img src="/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL.assets/image-20220728110301263.png" alt="image-20220728110301263"></p><p>所以接下来的思路就是从<code>AbstractMongoQuery#doExecute</code>出发，有没有没经过<code>ParameterBindingJsonReader&lt;init&gt;</code>走到<code>ParameterBindingJsonReader#bindableValueFor</code>的通路。</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">match</span>(source:<span class="keyword">Method</span>&#123;CLASSNAME:&quot;org.springframework.data.mongodb.repository.query.AbstractMongoQuery&quot;, NAME:&quot;doExecute&quot;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">match</span>((sink:<span class="keyword">Method</span>&#123;CLASSNAME:&quot;org.springframework.data.mongodb.util.json.ParameterBindingJsonReader&quot;, NAME:&quot;bindableValueFor&quot;&#125;) <span class="operator">&lt;</span><span class="operator">-</span> [:<span class="keyword">CALL</span><span class="operator">|</span>ALIAS] <span class="operator">-</span> (m:<span class="keyword">Method</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">call</span> apoc.algo.allSimplePaths(m, source, &quot;&lt;CALL|ALIAS&quot;,<span class="number">7</span>) yield path </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="operator">*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/tabby-Spring-Data-MongoDB-SPEL.assets/graph-16589767099012.png" alt="graph"></p><p>可以通过 decode 到 readBsonType 到想要点，然后根据 doExecute 调用节点寻找链</p><h3 id="StringBasedAggregation-doExecute"><a href="#StringBasedAggregation-doExecute" class="headerlink" title="StringBasedAggregation#doExecute"></a>StringBasedAggregation#doExecute</h3><p>当存在<code>@Aggregation</code>的注解（<strong>翻阅官方手册</strong>）即可走到这里</p><p><a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/mongodb/docs/current/reference/html/#mongodb.repositories.queries.aggregation">Aggregation文档</a> 和 <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/mongodb/docs/current/reference/html/#mongodb.repositories.queries.json-spel">SpEL文档</a></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Aggregation(&quot;&#123; &#x27;$project&#x27;: &#123; &#x27;_id&#x27; : #&#123;[0]&#125; &#125; &#125;&quot;)</span> </span><br><span class="line">List&lt;String&gt; <span class="title function_">findById</span><span class="params">(String keyword)</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="StringBasedMongoQuery-createQuery"><a href="#StringBasedMongoQuery-createQuery" class="headerlink" title="StringBasedMongoQuery#createQuery"></a>StringBasedMongoQuery#createQuery</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Query(&quot;&#123;id : ?#&#123;[0]&#125;&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line">Slice <span class="title function_">findById</span><span class="params">(String keyword)</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="AbstractMongoQuery-applyAnnotatedCollationIfPresent"><a href="#AbstractMongoQuery-applyAnnotatedCollationIfPresent" class="headerlink" title="AbstractMongoQuery#applyAnnotatedCollationIfPresent"></a>AbstractMongoQuery#applyAnnotatedCollationIfPresent</h3><p>和上面<code>createQuery()</code>于同一个函数触发的</p><h3 id="size"><a href="#size" class="headerlink" title="size"></a>size</h3><blockquote><p>只有<code>LazyBSONList</code>的<code>size()</code>才是gadget。而实际调用的是普通的<code>List</code>，无法触发</p></blockquote><p>最后注意一下[0]没有被替换为真实值，用?0会替换</p><h2 id="POC"><a href="#POC" class="headerlink" title="POC"></a>POC</h2><p>如果在该环境下有下述的注解：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Query(&quot;&#123;id : ?#&#123;?0&#125;&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Query(&quot;&#123;id : :#&#123;?0&#125;&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Aggregation(&quot;&#123; &#x27;$project&#x27;: &#123; &#x27;_id&#x27; : ?#&#123;?0&#125; &#125; &#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Aggregation(&quot;&#123; &#x27;$project&#x27;: &#123; &#x27;_id&#x27; : :#&#123;?0&#125; &#125; &#125;&quot;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可尝试注入</p><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><p><a href="https://tttang.com/archive/1647/">https://tttang.com/archive/1647/</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
