    <entry>
      <title>Dest0g3 ljcrt</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/26/Dest0g3-ljcrt/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/26/Dest0g3-ljcrt/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>师傅出的题真的很好，学到了什么叫“灵活处理”，以及在学习别人文章的时候要多思考（其实原本想到了能不能用反射的方法修改下值，但是一看见 new 了一个对象就觉得不行了，怎么没想到“修改源码”的方法呢）</p><p>回顾一下上篇文章的内容：</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/KpeDjIwvfBz61lL.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>为null是因为在该类的writeobject中：</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/lweZGavDM2JPmyB.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>new 了一个 ReferenceIndirector 的对象，序列化的是该对象 indirectFrom 方法返回的对象：</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/T6FSiXPlodNy2xg.png" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/kHfEzlIVOARML6q.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>所以之前说只有 var2 可控，但我们是不是忘了什么？</p><p>熟悉 PHP 反序列化的朋友知道序列化的数据其实重要的部分就是“属性值”，在 java 里应该就是师傅所说的修改字节码，我们可以不这么麻烦，完全可以<strong>仅修改 writeobject</strong> 方法就可以了。可以修改 C3P0 源码再重新生成 jar 包自己用（不太优雅，想想以前魔改 yso 也是这样的），然后就是师傅所说的利用 java agent 技术，算一次很好的再次实战，不了解的可以看看之前的文章：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/WDWAGAAFGAGDADSA/article/details/122270281">https://blog.csdn.net/WDWAGAAFGAGDADSA/article/details/122270281</a></p><h2 id="复现"><a href="#复现" class="headerlink" title="复现"></a>复现</h2><p>可以自己复制下师傅的 payload 生成 jar，也可以就用师傅的 jar 包</p><p>因为本来打算在 buu 上复现，所以稍微改一下 ip 之类的，然后点 project-structure -&gt; artifacts -&gt; add jar -&gt; from moudule</p><p>可以把师傅原来里面的</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/image-20220719090825872.png" alt="image-20220719090825872"></p><p>提取出来添加到依赖中，再修改一下MANIFEST.MF文件即可</p><p>我就采用preagent的方法了，将方法修改为</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/image-20220719102255851.png" alt="image-20220719102255851"></p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/image-20220719102330520.png" alt="image-20220719102330520"></p><p>运行时加上参数即可：</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/image-20220719102353815.png" alt="image-20220719102353815"></p><p>在两种加载代理的方法踩了许多坑：比如为什么静态时添加method方法体时一直报运行时错误；动态加载代理时一直是初始化失败；静态加载的应该是jar包却可以在源代码修改debug？本人不才，解决不了，只有修改源代码这一条路了</p><p>把mchange-commons源代码下载后用IDEA打开，添加三个依赖，编译成jar包，注意java版本，不然可能会有奇奇怪怪的错误，然后把它添加到原项目中</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/ltETxzrwRHJaCj7.png" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/3FXKYqZQ41Tys6C.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>然后记录一下一些命令</p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/AzndXEjqB2sHKhe.png" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="/Dest0g3-ljcrt.assets/sGMhupFIlytrOXL.png" alt="image.png"></p><p>虽然最后还是没有复现成功，但学到了很多经验</p><p>打算后来学习一下JNDIExploit这工具的写法，因为复现不成功总是因为搭建恶意RMIServer没有反应（做题已经遇见好几次了）</p><p>还有个点是不论是agent方法还是修改源代码，记得绕过一下ldap字符串的检测</p><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><p><a href="https://firebasky.github.io/2022/06/04/ljctr-wp/">https://firebasky.github.io/2022/06/04/ljctr-wp/</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 复现学习 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>HFCTF ezchain</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/25/HFCTF-ezchain/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/25/HFCTF-ezchain/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>此题对于学Java的同学的自动化代码审计，漏洞原理研究，Java本身机制了解有着一定的要求</p></blockquote><h2 id="分析"><a href="#分析" class="headerlink" title="分析"></a>分析</h2><p>题目不出网</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">version:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;2.4&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">services:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">nginx:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">nginx:1.15</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;0.0.0.0:8090:80&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">always</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">./nginx.conf:/etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf:ro</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">networks:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">internal_network</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">out_network</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">web:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">build:</span> <span class="string">./</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">always</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">./flag:/flag:ro</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">networks:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">internal_network</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">networks:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">internal_network:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">internal:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">ipam:</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">driver:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">out_network:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">ipam:</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">driver:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>反编译jar</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Index</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> Exception &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;server start&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">HttpServer</span> <span class="variable">server</span> <span class="operator">=</span> HttpServer.create(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">InetSocketAddress</span>(<span class="number">8090</span>), <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    server.createContext(<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">MyHandler</span>());</span><br><span class="line">    server.setExecutor(Executors.newCachedThreadPool());</span><br><span class="line">    server.start();</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">MyHandler</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">HttpHandler</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">handle</span><span class="params">(HttpExchange t)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> IOException &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">query</span> <span class="operator">=</span> t.getRequestURI().getQuery();</span><br><span class="line">      Map&lt;String, String&gt; queryMap = queryToMap(query);</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">response</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;Welcome to HFCTF 2022&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (queryMap != <span class="literal">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">token</span> <span class="operator">=</span> queryMap.get(<span class="string">&quot;token&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">secret</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;HFCTF2022&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (Objects.hashCode(token) == secret.hashCode() &amp;&amp; !secret.equals(token)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="type">InputStream</span> <span class="variable">is</span> <span class="operator">=</span> t.getRequestBody();</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">Hessian2Input</span> <span class="variable">input</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Hessian2Input</span>(is);</span><br><span class="line">            input.readObject();</span><br><span class="line">          &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (Exception e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            response = <span class="string">&quot;oops! something is wrong&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125; </span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          response = <span class="string">&quot;your token is wrong&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; </span><br><span class="line">      &#125; </span><br><span class="line">      t.sendResponseHeaders(<span class="number">200</span>, response.length());</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="type">OutputStream</span> <span class="variable">os</span> <span class="operator">=</span> t.getResponseBody();</span><br><span class="line">      os.write(response.getBytes());</span><br><span class="line">      os.close();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Map&lt;String, String&gt; <span class="title function_">queryToMap</span><span class="params">(String query)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (query == <span class="literal">null</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">null</span>; </span><br><span class="line">      Map&lt;String, String&gt; result = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">HashMap</span>&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">for</span> (String param : query.split(<span class="string">&quot;&amp;&quot;</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        String[] entry = param.split(<span class="string">&quot;=&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (entry.length &gt; <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          result.put(entry[<span class="number">0</span>], entry[<span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          result.put(entry[<span class="number">0</span>], <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; </span><br><span class="line">      &#125; </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> result;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首先先找个token吧，对于这种类型的题，我比较喜欢从String.hashcode源码出发构造：</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723142119122.png" alt="image-20220723142119122"></p><p>然后看反序列化处：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">Hessian2Input</span> <span class="variable">input</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Hessian2Input</span>(is);</span><br><span class="line">input.readObject();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还有rometools的依赖，所以是：利用<code>Hessian2</code>协议打<code>Rome</code>反序列化（反序列化map对象，后面会通过put操作，触发key的hashCode打Rome）</p><p>这里可以用curl传输字节序列？</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl --data-binary</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="SignedObject实现二次反序列化"><a href="#SignedObject实现二次反序列化" class="headerlink" title="SignedObject实现二次反序列化"></a>SignedObject实现二次反序列化</h3><p>在UnsafeDeserializer#getFieldMap中看到</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723155320443.png" alt="image-20220723155320443"></p><p>被transient修饰，或者静态变量是无法写入的，所以Rome常见的配合TemplatesImpl链打不通</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723155605009.png" alt="image-20220723155605009"></p><p>这个_tfactory为null（在反序列化时会调用其中的一个方法，为null就失败了）</p><blockquote><p>之后解决思路就是找个二次反序列化的点触发原生反序列化即可</p></blockquote><p>根据hessian的反序列化特性，要寻找无参构造函数，有getter方法的函数，且还要存在反序列化点</p><p>最后找到了java.security.SignedObject#SignedObject</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> Object <span class="title function_">getObject</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">throws</span> IOException, ClassNotFoundException</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// creating a stream pipe-line, from b to a</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">ByteArrayInputStream</span> <span class="variable">b</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ByteArrayInputStream</span>(<span class="built_in">this</span>.content);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">ObjectInput</span> <span class="variable">a</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ObjectInputStream</span>(b);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">Object</span> <span class="variable">obj</span> <span class="operator">=</span> a.readObject();</span><br><span class="line">    b.close();</span><br><span class="line">    a.close();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> obj;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>梳理下流程：</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723162921197.png" alt="image-20220723162921197"></p><p>会到getObject</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723162958492.png" alt="image-20220723162958492"></p><p>又通过这里可以看出</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723163100874.png" alt="image-20220723163100874"></p><p>反序列化的其实就是hashmap，最后会调用到TemplatesImpl的readObject（既然要反序列，肯定要“反序列化完全”）</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723182746852.png" alt="image-20220723182746852"></p><p>最后这里就赋值成功了（先完成的readObject再触发的key.hashCode，逻辑上也是对的）</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723162253198.png" alt="image-20220723162253198"></p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723183106128.png" alt="image-20220723183106128"></p><p>再补充一下有关TemplatesImpl的一些知识</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723183357303.png" alt="image-20220723183357303"></p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723184724401.png" alt="image-20220723184724401"></p><p>所以说</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220723184754767.png" alt="image-20220723184754767"></p><p>接下来注入一下内存马，（学习时间</p><blockquote><p>在一个运行中的应用里。所有所需要的类都可以从线程中获得</p></blockquote><p>暴力替换handler，代码可以移步y4师傅博客</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/5.png" alt="img"></p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/6.png" alt="img"></p><h3 id="UnixPrintService直接执行命令"><a href="#UnixPrintService直接执行命令" class="headerlink" title="UnixPrintService直接执行命令"></a>UnixPrintService直接执行命令</h3><p>参考marshalsec中hessian的链子好像可以不用实现反序列化接口，那就可以直接去找存在getter和命令执行的类了</p><blockquote><p><code>sun.print.UnixPrintService</code>的所有get方法都能触发</p></blockquote><p>均是通过命令拼接执行（Windows下没有这个？）</p><h2 id="如何寻找SignedObject"><a href="#如何寻找SignedObject" class="headerlink" title="如何寻找SignedObject"></a>如何寻找SignedObject</h2><h3 id="Tabby"><a href="#Tabby" class="headerlink" title="Tabby"></a>Tabby</h3><p>注意jdk的版本，不论是打包成jar还是运行</p><p>简单记录一下用法</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">match</span>(m1:<span class="keyword">Method</span>) <span class="keyword">where</span> m1.NAME <span class="operator">=</span><span class="operator">~</span> &quot;get.*&quot; <span class="keyword">and</span> m1.PARAMETER_SIZE<span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">return</span> m1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220725112228903.png" alt="image-20220725112228903"></p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220725105810490.png" alt="image-20220725105810490"></p><p>y4师傅的pyaload也就看的懂了</p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220725112131527.png" alt="image-20220725112131527"></p><p>这个工具的详细用法可以看</p><p><a href="https://github.com/wh1t3p1g/tabby/wiki/Tabby%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97">https://github.com/wh1t3p1g/tabby/wiki/Tabby%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97</a></p><p><a href="https://tttang.com/archive/1647/">https://tttang.com/archive/1647/</a></p><p><img src="/HFCTF-ezchain.assets/image-20220725112401589.png" alt="image-20220725112401589"></p><h3 id="CodeQL"><a href="#CodeQL" class="headerlink" title="CodeQL"></a>CodeQL</h3><p>有源码的情况下用起来还比较简单，大概思路就是下载openjdk然后编译生成数据库再去写sql语句查询吧，没有tabby方便</p><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><p><a href="https://y4tacker.github.io/2022/03/21/year/2022/3/2022%E8%99%8E%E7%AC%A6CTF-Java%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86/">https://y4tacker.github.io/2022/03/21/year/2022/3/2022%E8%99%8E%E7%AC%A6CTF-Java%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86/</a></p><p><a href="https://ha1c9on.top/?p=1973#0x02-tamplates">https://ha1c9on.top/?p=1973#0x02-tamplates</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
